od]]'' \u2013 Vanessa Walsh\n* ''[[Utawarerumono]]'' \u2013 Yuzuha\n* ''[[Welcome to the NHK]]'' \u2013 Megumi Kobayashi, Kazuko\n\n; 2008\n* ''[[Aquarion]]'' \u2013 Otoha\n* ''[[Black Blood Brothers]]'' \u2013 Kelly Wong\n* ''[[Claymore (manga)#Anime|Claymore]]'' \u2013 Miria\n* ''[[Darker than Black]]'' \u2013 Kanami Ishizaki<ref>{{cite episode | at=Closing credits | url=http://www.hulu.com/watch/139737#i0,p12,d0 | title=A Heart Unswaying On the Water's Surface, Part 1 | episodelink=List of Darker than Black episodes#ep13 | series=Darker Than Black | serieslink=Darker than Black | number=13 | via=Hulu | work=Funimation}}</ref>\n* ''[[Ghost Hunt]]'' \u2013 Madoka Mori\n* ''[[Magikano]]'' \u2013 Michiru Mamiya\n* ''[[Moonlight Mile (manga)|Moonlight Mile]]'' \u2013 Riyoko Ikeuchi\n* ''[[Shattered Angels]]'' \u2013 Kaon\n\n; 2009\n* ''[[Baccano!]]'' \u2013 Chane Laforet\n* ''[[Bamboo Blade]]'' \u2013 Reimi Odajima\n* ''[[Big Windup!]]'' \u2013 Ruri Mihashi\n* ''[[Blassreiter]]'' \u2013 Elea\n* ''[[D.Gray-Man]]'' \u2013 [[Lulu Bell]], Lero\n* ''[[Evangelion: 1.0 You Are (Not) Alone]]'' \u2013 Pen Pen\n* ''[[Heroic Age (anime)|Heroic Age]]'' \u2013 Tail Ol Mehelim, Mail Al Mehelim\n* ''[[Kaze no Stigma]]'' \u2013 Misao Ogami\n* ''[[Kenichi: The Mightiest Disciple]]'' \u2013 Number 20\n* ''[[Murder Princess]]'' \u2013 Milano Entolasia/Alita Forland, Falis\n* ''[[Mamotte! Lollipop|Save Me! Lollipop]]'' \u2013 San\n* ''[[Sgt. Frog]]'' \u2013 [[List of Sgt. Frog characters#Momoka Nishizawa|Momoka Nishizawa]]\n* ''[[Strain: Strategic Armored Infantry]]'' \u2013 Becky\n* ''[[The Tower of Druaga (anime)|The Tower of Druaga]] series'' \u2013 Coopa\n| {{dts|2009}} || ''[[Tears to Tiara]]'' || Octavia || Anime Network ||\n; 2010\n* ''[[Blue Drop]]'' \u2013 Hagino Senkoji (Ekaril)\n* ''[[Dragon Ball: Curse of the Blood Rubies]]'' \u2013 Bulma\n* ''[[Ghost Hound]]'' \u2013 Himeko Ogami\n* ''[[Hero Tales]]'' \u2013 Enki\n* ''[[Hetalia Axis Powers]]'' \u2013 Belarus, Flying Mint Bun