ls]]'' || [[Parasite Dolls#Main cast|Reiko Michaelson]] || || <ref>{{cite AV media | title=[[Parasite Dolls]] | time=credits, English cast | medium=DVD | year=2004 }}</ref>\n|-\n|2005\n|''[[Those Who Hunt Elves]]''\n|Bruno, Presiding Judge\n|Season 2\n|<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2005-01-01/march-2005-adv-releases|title=March 2005 ADV Releases|work=Anime News Network|access-date=2018-02-24|language=en}}</ref>\n|-\n| {{dts|2005}} ||  ''[[A Tree of Palme]]'' ||  Mu || || <ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mania.com/tree-palme-english-cast-list_article_84743.html|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081204201538/http://www.mania.com/tree-palme-english-cast-list_article_84743.html|title=Tree of Palme English Cast List|date=November 15, 2004|archivedate=December 4, 2008|work=Mania.com|accessdate=November 3, 2015|url-status=dead}}</ref>\n|-\n| {{dts|2005}} || ''[[Burst Angel]]'' || [[Burst Angel#Jo|Jo]] || || <ref>{{cite journal |first=Chris |last=Johnston |title=City of Angels |journal=Newtype USA |volume=4 |issue=4 |year=2005 |pages=34\u201335 }}</ref><ref name=\"burst angel review\"/>\n|-\n| {{dts|2005}} || ''[[Ghost Stories (anime)|Ghost Stories]]'' || [[Ghost Stories (anime)#Momoko Koigakubo|Momoko Koigakubo]] || || <ref name=\"activeanime 2006\"/>\n|-\n| {{dts|2005}} || ''[[Godannar]]'' || Mira Ackerman || || <ref name=\"activeanime 2006\"/>\n|-\n| {{dts|2005}} || ''[[Gunslinger Girl]]'' || [[List of Gunslinger Girl characters#Angelica|Angelica]] || || <ref name=\"btva\"/>\n|-\n| {{dts|2005}} || ''[[Initial D]]'' || [[List of Initial D characters and teams#Sayuki|Sayuki]] || Funimation dub <!-- Funimation credits --> || <ref name=\"btva\"/>\n|-\n| {{dts|2005}} || ''[[Kodocha]]'' || [[List of Kodocha characters#Aya Sugita|Aya Sugita]] || <!-- Funimation closing credits --> ||\n|-\n| {{dts|2006}} ||  ''[[Rumbling Hearts]]'' || [[Rumbling Hearts#Mayu Tamano|Mayu Tamano]] || || <ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/review/rumbling-hearts/dvd-1|date=December 26, 2006|first=Theron|last=Martin|title=Rumbling Hearts DVD 1 \u2013 Review|work=Anime News Network}}</ref>\n|-\n| {{dts|2006|12|19|format=y}} || ''[[Black Cat (manga)|Black Cat]]'' || [[List of Black Cat characters#Kyoko Kirisaki|Kyoko Kirisaki]] || || <ref>{{cite episode | series=Black Cat | serieslink=Black Cat (manga) | title=The Kitty Cat | number=14 | publisher=Funimation | time=Closing credits, Cast }}</ref>\n|-\n|2006\n|''[[D.Gray-man]]''\n|Lero, [[List of D.Gray-man characters#Lulu Bell|Lulu Bell]], Chomesuke\n|\n|\n|-\n| {{dts|2006}} || ''[[Gatchaman]]'' || || ADR script writer || <ref name=\"activeanime 2006\"/>\n|-\n| {{dts|2006}} || ''[[Madlax]]'' || || ADR script writer || <ref name=\"my voice acting uk interview 2006\">{{cite web|url=http://my.voiceacting.co.uk/site/2008/02/18/interview-with-monica-rial-and-chris-patton-amecon-2006|title=Interview with Monica Rial and Chris Patton Amecon 2006|publisher=voiceacting.co.uk|date=February 18, 2008|accessdate=August 21, 2014}}</ref><ref name=\"activeanime 2006\"/>\n|-\n| {{dts|2006}} || ''[[Nanaka 6/17]]'' || [[Nanaka 6/17#Nanaka Kirisato|Nanaka Kirisato]] || || <ref>{{cite episode | series= Nanaka 6/17 | serieslink= Nanaka 6/17 | number=1 | at=Closing credits, Cast }}</ref>\n|-\n| {{dts|2006}} || ''[[Negima!]]'' || [[List of Negima! Magister Negi Magi characters#Konoka Konoe|Konoka Konoe]], [[List of Negima! Magister Negi Magi characters#Kazumi Asakura|Kazumi Asakura]], [[List of Negima! Magister Negi Magi characters#Satsuki Yotsuba|Satsuki Yosuba]] || Also ''[[Negima!?]]'' <!-- Funimation credits --> || <ref>{{cite episode | series=Negima! | serieslink=Negima! | number=1 | at=Closing credits, Cast }}</ref>\n|-\n| {{dts|2006}} || ''[[Shin-chan]]'' || [[List of Crayon Shin-chan characters#Ai Suotome|Ai Suotome]] || Funimation dub || <ref name=\"otakunews 2006\"/>\n|-\n| {{dts|2006}} || ''[[Speed Grapher]]'' || [[List of Speed Grapher characters#Kagura Tenn\u014dzu|Kagura Ten